    <text id="B0363T">
        <front id="d2">
            <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                <p>Smiley asks Jackson to help him get an extension on some of his debts, because he
                    is disabled and does not want to lose his livestock to pay the debt.</p>
            </div1>
        </front>

        <body id="d4">
            <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
                <head>
                    <name type="recipient">Mr Jackson or Tukey</name>
                </head>

                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <date value="1867-06-24">June 24th 1867</date>
                        <name type="place">Staunton Augusta <abbr expan="County">Co</abbr>
                            <abbr expan="Virginia">Va</abbr></name>
                    </dateline>
                    <salute>Dear Sir</salute>
                </opener>

                <p>I wish to call on you to confer me the favor that I ask if you have it in your
                    power to grant to me &amp; that is as follows:</p>

                <p>I hereby certify that I am a cripple By Accident &amp; have a large <orig
                        reg="family">famly</orig> to <orig reg="surport">surport</orig> Also I am in
                    Debt &amp; sued for the sum of forty six Dollars &amp; have given a
                    Delivery Bond on my cow &amp; sow &amp; pig. I dont want my securities
                    to suffer as I can pay the Debt myself if I get longer Indulgence &amp; that
                    is the favor I now Ask for time until the first day of November 1867.</p>

                <closer>
                    <salute>given from under my hand &amp;c</salute>
                    <signed>Alex Smiley</signed>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
    </text>
